channel.title: Removing uncooking pot and the cat things
channel.description:
Hey, mr eak here (was named Obliterscape)
Okay well how do i remove the uncooking pot and the cat things off the island? i must sound like a stupid question but i cant work it out
i know uncooking pot id is 8985 and i cant find it in any files
so if and one could help thanks :)

item.title: Removing uncooking pot and the cat things
item.dc:creator: @Skype1 Skype™
item.description:
@Skype1 wrote:

Look for Deltethatobject in your client.java (If you are using Delta) and copy them and edit the two ID’s and insert the Xcoord and Ycoord of the object you wish to delete.
